21-01-03T10:25:55.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:27:26.000Z","msg":"Google過 有人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"聽講之後佢死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b5a8313ffae655a23d84aed06fce417caa8ab9","tid":2351560,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:28:42.000Z","msg":"下次直接打入子宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12be39afc7b7cff87fe74871f67dcc7d3fcc4256","tid":2351560,"uid":51583,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1fe08e9a67e565928e3882850c68dbcd10c3e99d","tid":2351560,"uid":331838,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"咩宜家男人都有得打咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:28:45.000Z","msg":"好多年啦<br />\n好多男人都有打"},{"pid":"a299cf9877596608011f468399cfe72ada294a4a","tid":2351560,"uid":223912,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"1fe08e9a67e565928e3882850c68dbcd10c3e99d","tid":2351560,"uid":331838,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:26:02.000Z","msg":"咩宜家男人都有得打咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:29:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其實hpv男女都可以打<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人都要打子宮頸癌針？<br />\n<br />\n24 Jun 2019<br />\n<br />\n蔡沛恒博士<br />\n香港大學李嘉誠醫學院<br />\n護理學院助理教授<br />\n<br />\n說起子宮頸癌疫苗，相信普羅大眾都不會覺得陌生，但其正確名稱應為人類乳頭瘤病毒（HPV）疫苗。HPV是全球最常見透過性接觸傳染的病毒，可引致子宮頸、肛門、外陰、陰道及陰莖的癌前病變及癌症。<br />\n<br />\n雖然不時在坊間接觸到HPV疫苗的推廣資訊，但廣告總是打著「子宮頸癌疫苗」的旗號，標籤HPV為「女人病」，令大眾誤以為HPV疫苗是女性專屬。其實此病是透過性接觸傳染，因此男女雙方同時接種疫苗，才能大大減低HPV病毒的感染，降低患上性病及生殖器官癌症的風險。現時，香港共有三款已註冊的HPV疫苗，分別為2價、4價及9價疫苗，後兩者可供男性接種。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7934bf343a79b3015ce84e7e880531fedd50a267","tid":2351560,"uid":223912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e2a678b5cf7711e5e50d01212a6029e3ac6f1a80","tid":2351560,"uid":317749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ddada77b905ffe4bf6d3af05935c28ae375f9394","tid":2351560,"uid":223912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"03d0a7186a299630f64d0b126db934555ed6a65a","tid":2351560,"uid":317749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:25:55.000Z","msg":"下世小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:27:26.000Z","msg":"Google過 有人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:27:58.000Z","msg":"聽講之後佢死咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:29:29.000Z","msg":"我唔準你咁講<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4f2909e3c66ca78bc57a24500d34d6acbd7f0d1","tid":2351560,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-03T10:30:10.000Z","msg":"唔識問醫生？"},{"pid":"e3f1a6bda19106ea961b111403f6a05f7303cbf8","tid":2351560,"uid":317749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7934bf343a79b3015ce84e7e880531fedd50a267","tid":2351560,"uid":223912,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e2a678b5cf7711e5e50d01212a6029e3ac6f1a80","tid":2351560,"uid":317749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc